high_descs: Move to the left side of the brown end table with the lamp that is directly in front you.
Pick up the white cell phone that is on the top of the stand.
Move back around to the front of the stand in front of you with the lamp.
Open the top drawer. Place the cell phone inside. close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Move the cell phone from the top of an end table to the top drawer.

high_descs: Turn left then face the night stand where the phone is on top of the night stand
Pick up the phone on top of the night stand
Carry the phone to face the drawer of the wooden night stand
Place the phone inside of the drawer then shut the drawer
anns.task_desc: Place a phone in the night stand drawer

high_descs: Move to the left and turn to face the left side of the dresser with the phone on it.
Pick the phone up from the dresser.
Back up and turn to face the side of the dresser with the lamp.
Open the top drawer and put the phone in and shut the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put a phone in a drawer.
